<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>For Vien 💖</title>

<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .card {
        width: 360px;
        height: 450px;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        overflow: hidden;
        position: relative;
        cursor: pointer;
    }

    .front, .inside {
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        transition: all 1s ease;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    /* Front (Click me page) */
    .front {
        background: #ff6f91;
        color: white;
        z-index: 2;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    /* Inside message */
    .inside {
        background: #fff8f8;
        color: #ff4f7a;
        transform: translateY(100%);
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .card.open .front {
        transform: translateY(-100%);
    }

    .card.open .inside {
        transform: translateY(0);
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 1.8em;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 1em;
        line-height: 1.5em;
    }

    .click {
        font-size: 1.5em;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="card" onclick="openCard()" id="card">

    <!-- FRONT -->
    <div class="front">
        <div class="click">Click me 💌</div>
    </div>

    <!-- INSIDE -->
    <div class="inside">
        <h1>🎉 Happy Birthday Vien ❤️</h1>
        <p>
            I just wanna say I love you.<br><br>
            I really enjoy being with you, and I’m always happy when it’s you.<br><br>
            I look forward to doing more things with you — simple days, random moments, everything.<br><br>
            I hope you achieve all your dreams. I’ll always be here supporting you.<br><br>
            I’m really glad it’s you. 💖
        </p>
    </div>

</div>

<script>
function openCard() {
    document.getElementById("card").classList.add("open");
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
